DDeessccrriippttiioonn
       These  functions  manipulate  the window attributes of the
       current or specified window.

       The and functions turn off attrs in the current or  speci-
       fied window without affecting any others.

       The  and  functions turn on attrs in the current or speci-
       fied window without affecting any others.

       The and functions set the  background  attributes  of  the
       current or specified window to attrs.

